@startuml
[*] --> RegistrationState
RegistrationState --> RegisteredState : registration success
RegistrationState --> EndAccessState : registration failed

RegisteredState --> SignInState : sign in request
SignInState --> AccessGrantedState : valid credentials
SignInState --> EndAccessState : invalid credentials

AccessGrantedState --> FacilitiesState : access granted
FacilitiesState --> NewsAndExpertContentState : facilities accessed
NewsAndExpertContentState --> HealthInfoState : news and expert content viewed
HealthInfoState --> ContinueOrFinishState : health information result viewed
ContinueOrFinishState --> FacilitiesState : continue using system
ContinueOrFinishState --> EndSessionState : finish session

AccessGrantedState --> FinanceServicesState : finance-related services accessed
FinanceServicesState --> InsuranceValidationState : insurance validation required
InsuranceValidationState --> PaymentProcessingState : payment processing started
PaymentProcessingState --> CheckPaymentWithInsuranceState : check payment with insurance
CheckPaymentWithInsuranceState --> CompletePaymentProcessState : payment completed

AccessGrantedState --> PurchaseState : purchase request
PurchaseState --> SelectPaymentMethodState : select payment method
SelectPaymentMethodState --> CashPaymentDetailsState : cash payment selected
CashPaymentDetailsState --> CompletePaymentProcessState : complete payment process
SelectPaymentMethodState --> InsuranceBasedPaymentState : insurance-based payment selected
InsuranceBasedPaymentState --> CompletePaymentProcessState : complete payment process

PurchaseState --> CollectFeedbackState : service completed
CollectFeedbackState --> EndSessionState : log out user
EndSessionState --> [*] : logged out

EndAccessState --> [*] : access ended

@enduml
